                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090920-87-off500 t18090920-87-cd501"></join>, a gelding, value 40 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18090920-87-victim889" type="victimName">
                     Mary 
                     Hinton
